移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1773193639345}},"smart_blocks:试卷汇总/10-试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06753193,-0.00997382,0.03956154,-0.06684722,-0.00462137,0.01823671,0.01344634,-0.02328788,0.03019216,-0.00075508,0.023884,-0.03695892,0.05016258,-0.00184328,0.02669477,0.03906433,-0.0244724,-0.0212407,-0.09876686,-0.00002935,0.15849389,-0.02602455,-0.00199144,-0.06601624,0.03977584,0.0413544,0.01173318,-0.01721349,-0.01669914,-0.17963059,-0.00254847,0.00937344,0.00996636,0.04053136,0.04214056,-0.06735308,-0.01995991,0.06245863,-0.07793171,0.04435351,-0.00510759,0.0726715,0.0577893,-0.02581909,0.01744513,-0.0342735,-0.01696044,-0.03164947,0.02448008,-0.03863535,-0.0469963,-0.01673594,-0.02474117,0.03433708,0.03181693,-0.01718603,-0.01442323,0.07788644,0.03751689,-0.03915829,0.04860689,0.00715636,-0.21466413,0.00195864,0.05450689,-0.01349866,-0.01012439,-0.03618231,0.04628361,0.05370939,-0.04423722,0.02605801,0.02861511,0.04594804,-0.01120778,-0.0230661,0.03026052,-0.00604451,-0.08432643,-0.01993025,-0.0190613,0.08659569,0.03015502,0.00791764,-0.00322434,0.00341177,0.00794146,-0.05536331,-0.0179425,-0.04644666,-0.00100126,-0.01079072,0.01130222,0.05507538,-0.0446621,-0.00073811,0.03315865,0.02912692,-0.02848423,0.09727915,-0.03563372,0.08095709,-0.01449321,-0.10360382,0.00583512,-0.05920265,-0.0447236,-0.07316427,-0.04783764,-0.03360358,-0.03811092,-0.02326987,0.07489141,-0.0692471,-0.01236015,-0.00794484,0.06822664,0.03810109,-0.02417753,-0.02028465,0.03884853,0.05798984,0.02836405,-0.04674513,-0.01025967,-0.06149958,0.03059916,-0.0059906,0.06055684,0.06659999,0.03981839,-0.01268543,0.04062592,0.02380756,-